descriptionHtml:
Power Browser is empowering super fast, secure . Now with private search, smart downloader, night mode, AI technology, and so much more!

✔ Browse fast with compression algorithms
✔ Industry leading privacy and security
✔ Personalised feed, fast local news & funny video
✔ Customised shortcut, colour & interface
✔ Offline mode, file sharing
✔ Smart downloader for online video, music, file
✔ Incognito search, privately browse
✔ Multiple tab management
✔ Built-in ad blocker
✔ Brave search
✔ AI technology

• Private Browser
Power Browser is a secure browser providing you with great privacy protection on the web. Use private tabs to browse incognito & browse privately without leaving a trace on your device or being tracked.

• Fast Browsing around the World
With local Power Browser data centres, you have one of the fastest and most reliable connections when using the web browser.

• Smart Downloader
Power Browser effortlessly scans websites fast for awesome video and music treasures, swiftly snatching them and downloading in the background for you. Rediscover all your past downloads and unearth any private files on your device with ease.

• Video Player
Watch & listen live, or download for later. Opera Mini’s video player has a one-handed mode for easy operations on mobile, and is integrated with your Download Manager.

• Customise Your Private Browser
You are the Master of Power Browser! Customise the private browser by choosing your favourite layout, theme, news categories and more. Make your Power Browser stand out!

• Night Mode
Dim your screen and protect your eyes when reading in the dark with Opera Mini’s night mode.

• Block Ads
Power Browser has a native built-in ad blocker so you can surf the web without annoying ads. Ad Block brings you a completely fast & private web browsing experience!
